title: Coffee1st
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe style menu with mainly vegetarian and vegan food. Vegan choices include the lentil and veggie burger, spelt curry pie, funky chunky pie, spinach patizie, focaccia, funky beans, spinach and tofu quiche, funky fudge brownie, coconut cakes with raspberry filling, and peanut butter cupcakes. Gluten free options. Uses only vegan butter. Relaxed casual atmosphere with lounge in back and Wi-Fi. Also has a barista training school on premises.
